flowchart LR
    A[Upload or record audio] --> B[Validate file]
    B --> C[Decode audio]
    C --> D[Mono 16 kHz]
    D --> E[First 5 seconds]
    E --> F[Extract 227 features]
    F --> G[Saved StandardScaler]
    G --> H[Saved XGBoost classifier]
    H --> I[Fake and real probabilities]
    I --> J[Three-way decision]
    F --> K[Grouped acoustic evidence]
    C --> L[Waveform and spectrogram]
    J --> M[JSON report and UI result]
    K --> M
    L --> M

